      • configure

        public ColorHistogramOp configure(int[] chans,
                         int[] histsize,
                         float[] ranges)
        Configure the HistorgramOperation. The default is set for use of RGB images
        Parameters:
        chans - list with channal id's default = {0, 1, 2}
        histsize - for each channel the number of bins to use, default = {255, 255 ,255}
        ranges - for each channel the min. and max. values present, default = {0, 256, 0, 256, 0, 256 }
        See Also:
        OpenCV Documentation
